Package ohos.data.resultset

Class CombinedResultSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.data.resultset.AbsResultSet
      • ohos.data.resultset.CombinedResultSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ResultSet

    public class CombinedResultSet
extends AbsResultSet
    Represents a linear result set that combines multiple result sets.

    Different types of result sets can be combined in a CombinedResultSet. When the getAllColumnNames() or getColumnTypeForIndex(int) method is called, column names or the column type in the original result set matching the row of the CombinedResultSet is returned.

    Since:
    3
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.Data#DATA_APPDATAMGR
